  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "md-step2",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 🧠 第二步：接入大脑——初始化 LLM\n",
    "\n",
    "林泽远知道，光有数学公式还不够。他需要一个「大脑」——一个能理解人类语言、会规划任务、会调用工具的语言模型。\n",
    "\n",
    "他选择了 DeepSeek，将 API Key 存入 `.env` 文件，然后初始化模型。\n",
    "\n",
    "> **💡 概念：LLM 在 Agent 中扮演什么角色？**\n",
    ">\n",
    "> LLM 是 Agent 的「规划者」和「决策者」。它接收用户的问题，理解意图，然后决定：\n",
    "> - 现在应该调用哪个工具？\n",
    "> - 工具的参数应该是什么？\n",
    "> - 工具的结果怎么解读？\n",
    "> - 什么时候可以给出最终答案？"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "code-llm",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "load_dotenv()  # 从 .env 文件加载环境变量（包含 DEEPSEEK_API_KEY）\n",
    "\n",
    "llm = ChatDeepSeek(\n",
    "    model='deepseek-chat',\n",
    "    api_key=os.getenv('DEEPSEEK_API_KEY'),\n",
    "    temperature=0,  # temperature=0：让模型输出更确定、更稳定（适合工具调用场景）\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'✅ 大脑上线！模型：{llm.model_name}')\n",
    "print('林泽远感觉到了一种前所未有的力量——他不再孤单地面对数据，他有了一个会思考的伙伴。')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "md-step3",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 🔧 第三步：打造工具（Tools）——Agent 的双手\n",
    "\n",
    "LLM 是大脑，但它本身无法下载数据、无法做矩阵运算。\n",
    "\n",
    "林泽远需要给这个大脑装上 **双手**——也就是「工具（Tools）」。\n",
    "\n",
    "在 LangChain 中，任何普通的 Python 函数，只需加上 `@tool` 装饰器，就能变成 Agent 可以调用的工具。\n",
    "\n",
    "> **💡 概念：什么是 Tool？**\n",
    ">\n",
    "> Tool 是 Agent 与外部世界交互的接口。LLM 本身是「封闭」的——它不能上网、不能读文件、不能调 API。\n",
    "> Tool 打破了这个封闭，让 Agent 能够：\n",
    "> - 获取实时数据\n",
    "> - 执行计算\n",
    "> - 调用外部服务\n",
    ">\n",
    "> LangChain 通过 `@tool` 装饰器，自动从函数的**类型注解**和 **docstring** 中提取工具描述，\n",
    "> 告诉 LLM「这个工具能做什么、参数是什么意思」。**所以 docstring 一定要写清楚！**\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "#### 工具一：数据下载器"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "code-tool-download",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 工具之间共享数据的「仓库」——一个简单的全局字典\n",
    "# 工具1 把数据存进来，工具2 从这里读取\n",
    "_portfolio_data: dict = {}\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "def _a_code_to_yahoo(code: str) -> str:\n",
    "    \"\"\"A 股代码转 Yahoo Finance 格式。\"\"\"\n",
    "    if code.startswith('6'):\n",
    "        return f'{code}.SS'\n",
    "    elif code.startswith(('0', '3')):\n",
    "        return f'{code}.SZ'\n",
    "    elif code.startswith(('4', '8')):\n",
    "        return f'{code}.BJ'\n",
    "    return code\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "def _download_price_data(codes: list, start_date: str, end_date: str,\n",
    "                          market: str = 'US') -> 'pd.DataFrame | str':\n",
    "    \"\"\"内部函数：下载收盘价并计算日收益率。\"\"\"\n",
    "    if market.upper() == 'A':\n",
    "        yahoo_codes = [_a_code_to_yahoo(c) for c in codes]\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        yahoo_codes = codes\n",
    "\n",
    "    start = pd.to_datetime(start_date, format='%Y%m%d').strftime('%Y-%m-%d')\n",
    "    end   = pd.to_datetime(end_date,   format='%Y%m%d').strftime('%Y-%m-%d')\n",
    "\n",
    "    try:\n",
    "        raw = yf.download(yahoo_codes, start=start, end=end,\n",
    "                          progress=False, auto_adjust=True)\n",
    "        if raw.empty:\n",
    "            return json.dumps({'错误': '返回数据为空，请检查股票代码和日期范围'}, ensure_ascii=False)\n",
    "\n",
    "        # 兼容 yfinance 多股/单股的不同列结构\n",
    "        if isinstance(raw.columns, pd.MultiIndex):\n",
    "            close = raw['Close']\n",
    "            close.columns = codes\n",
    "        else:\n",
    "            price_col = 'Close' if 'Close' in raw.columns else 'Adj Close'\n",
    "            close = raw[[price_col]].rename(columns={price_col: codes[0]})\n",
    "\n",
    "        returns = close.dropna(how='all').pct_change().dropna()\n",
    "        if len(returns) < 5:\n",
    "            return json.dumps({'错误': '有效数据不足 5 条，请检查参数'}, ensure_ascii=False)\n",
    "        return returns\n",
    "\n",
    "    except Exception as e:\n",
    "        return json.dumps({'错误': f'下载失败：{e}'}, ensure_ascii=False)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "@tool\n",
    "def download_stock_data(\n",
    "    stock_codes: str,\n",
    "    market: str = 'US',\n",
    "    start_date: str = '20240101',\n",
    "    end_date: str = '20241231',\n",
    ") -> str:\n",
    "    '''下载股票历史行情数据并计算日收益率，支持 A 股和美股。\n",
    "\n",
    "    Args:\n",
    "        stock_codes: 股票代码，多只用英文逗号分隔。\n",
    "                     A股示例：000001,600519,300750\n",
    "                     美股示例：AAPL,MSFT,GOOGL\n",
    "        market: 市场类型，A 表示 A 股，US 表示美股，默认 US\n",
    "        start_date: 起始日期，格式 YYYYMMDD，默认 20240101\n",
    "        end_date:   结束日期，格式 YYYYMMDD，默认 20241231\n",
    "\n",
    "    Returns:\n",
    "        数据下载状态及基本统计摘要（JSON 字符串）\n",
    "    '''\n",
    "    codes = [c.strip() for c in stock_codes.split(',')]\n",
    "    returns_df = _download_price_data(codes, start_date, end_date, market)\n",
    "\n",
    "    if isinstance(returns_df, str):  # 出错时返回错误信息字符串\n",
    "        return returns_df\n",
    "\n",
    "    # ✅ 将数据存入共享仓库，供后续工具使用\n",
    "    _portfolio_data['returns'] = returns_df\n",
    "    _portfolio_data['stocks']  = codes\n",
    "    _portfolio_data['market']  = market.upper()\n",
    "\n",
    "    summary = {\n",
    "        '状态': '下载成功',\n",
    "        '市场': 'A股' if market.upper() == 'A' else '美股',\n",
    "        '股票代码': codes,\n",
    "        '有效交易日数': len(returns_df),\n",
    "        '日期范围': f'{str(returns_df.index[0])[:10]} 至 {str(returns_df.index[-1])[:10]}',\n",
    "        '各股年化收益率（估算）': {\n",
    "            code: f'{returns_df[code].mean() * 252:.2%}' for code in codes\n",
    "        },\n",
    "        '提示': '数据已保存，可调用 markowitz_optimize 进行马科维茨优化',\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    return json.dumps(summary, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "print('✅ 工具一「数据下载器」制造完毕')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "md-tool2-intro",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### 工具二：马科维茨优化器\n",
    "\n",
    "这是林泽远最引以为豪的工具。\n",
    "\n",
    "**马科维茨理论的核心思想（1952）：**\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\text{最大化夏普比率} = \\frac{E[R_p] - R_f}{\\sigma_p} = \\frac{\\mathbf{w}^\\top \\boldsymbol{\\mu} - R_f}{\\sqrt{\\mathbf{w}^\\top \\boldsymbol{\\Sigma} \\mathbf{w}}}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "其中：\n",
    "- $\\mathbf{w}$：权重向量（我们要优化的目标）\n",
    "- $\\boldsymbol{\\mu}$：各资产预期收益率向量\n",
    "- $\\boldsymbol{\\Sigma}$：协方差矩阵（衡量资产间的风险关联）\n",
    "- $R_f$：无风险利率\n",
    "\n",
    "关键就在这个 $\\boldsymbol{\\Sigma}$。**怎么估计它，决定了一切。**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "code-tool-markowitz",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "@tool\n",
    "def markowitz_optimize(risk_free_rate: float = 0.02) -> str:\n",
    "    '''对已下载的股票数据进行马科维茨投资组合优化（经典方法）。\n",
    "\n",
    "    核心方法：用历史日收益率的样本协方差矩阵估计风险，再通过\n",
    "    scipy 数值优化求解最大夏普比率组合和最小方差组合。\n",
    "\n",
    "    请先调用 download_stock_data 下载数据后再使用此工具。\n",
    "\n",
    "    Args:\n",
    "        risk_free_rate: 年化无风险利率，默认 0.02（2%）。美股建议 0.045。\n",
    "\n",
    "    Returns:\n",
    "        两种最优组合的权重及风险收益指标（JSON 字符串）\n",
    "    '''\n",
    "    if 'returns' not in _portfolio_data:\n",
    "        return '错误：请先调用 download_stock_data 下载数据。'\n",
    "\n",
    "    returns_df = _portfolio_data['returns']\n",
    "    stocks     = _portfolio_data['stocks']\n",
    "    n          = len(stocks)\n",
    "\n",
    "    mean_ret = returns_df.mean().values\n",
    "    # ⚠️ 关键步骤：用「样本协方差矩阵」估计 Σ，然后年化\n",
    "    cov_mat  = returns_df.cov().values * 252\n",
    "\n",
    "    constraints = [{'type': 'eq', 'fun': lambda w: np.sum(w) - 1}]\n",
    "    bounds = [(0.0, 1.0)] * n\n",
    "    w0     = np.ones(n) / n  # 等权重作为初始点\n",
    "\n",
    "    def neg_sharpe(w):\n",
    "        ret = float(np.dot(w, mean_ret) * 252)\n",
    "        vol = float(np.sqrt(w @ cov_mat @ w))\n",
    "        return -(ret - risk_free_rate) / vol\n",
    "\n",
    "    def port_vol(w):\n",
    "        return float(np.sqrt(w @ cov_mat @ w))\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 用 scipy 的 SLSQP 算法求解约束最优化\n",
    "    res_sr = minimize(neg_sharpe, w0, method='SLSQP',\n",
    "                      bounds=bounds, constraints=constraints)\n",
    "    res_mv = minimize(port_vol,   w0, method='SLSQP',\n",
    "                      bounds=bounds, constraints=constraints)\n",
    "\n",
    "    def stats(w):\n",
    "        ret = float(np.dot(w, mean_ret) * 252)\n",
    "        vol = float(np.sqrt(w @ cov_mat @ w))\n",
    "        return ret, vol, (ret - risk_free_rate) / vol\n",
    "\n",
    "    sr_ret, sr_vol, sr_sharpe = stats(res_sr.x)\n",
    "    mv_ret, mv_vol, mv_sharpe = stats(res_mv.x)\n",
    "\n",
    "    result = {\n",
    "        '方法': '马科维茨经典方法（样本协方差矩阵估计）',\n",
    "        '最大夏普比率组合（激进型）': {\n",
    "            '权重配置': {stocks[i]: f'{res_sr.x[i]:.2%}' for i in range(n)},\n",
    "            '年化预期收益': f'{sr_ret:.2%}',\n",
    "            '年化波动率（风险）': f'{sr_vol:.2%}',\n",
    "            '夏普比率': round(sr_sharpe, 4),\n",
    "        },\n",
    "        '最小方差组合（保守型）': {\n",
    "            '权重配置': {stocks[i]: f'{res_mv.x[i]:.2%}' for i in range(n)},\n",
    "            '年化预期收益': f'{mv_ret:.2%}',\n",
    "            '年化波动率（风险）': f'{mv_vol:.2%}',\n",
    "            '夏普比率': round(mv_sharpe, 4),\n",
    "        },\n",
    "        '参数说明': f'无风险利率 {risk_free_rate:.1%}，基于 {len(returns_df)} 个交易日历史数据',\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    return json.dumps(result, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "print('✅ 工具二「马科维茨优化器」制造完毕')\n",
    "print('林泽远满意地看着这两个工具，心想：万事俱备，只欠东风。')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "md-step4",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 🤖 第四步：组装智能体——让大脑和双手连接起来\n",
    "\n",
    "现在，林泽远要把 LLM（大脑）和 Tools（双手）组合成一个完整的 Agent。\n",
    "\n",
    "> **💡 概念：Agent 的工作原理是什么？**\n",
    ">\n",
    "> LangChain 的 Agent 基于 **ReAct（Reasoning + Acting）** 框架运行：\n",
    ">\n",
    "> ```\n",
    "> 用户提问\n",
    ">     ↓\n",
    "> [思考] LLM 分析问题，决定下一步行动\n",
    ">     ↓\n",
    "> [行动] 调用某个 Tool，传入参数\n",
    ">     ↓\n",
    "> [观察] 接收 Tool 的返回结果\n",
    ">     ↓\n",
    "> [思考] 基于结果再次规划...\n",
    ">     ↓\n",
    "> ... 循环，直到 LLM 认为可以给出最终答案 ...\n",
    ">     ↓\n",
    "> [最终答案] 返回给用户\n",
    "> ```\n",
    ">\n",
    "> `create_agent` 帮我们把这一切串联起来，我们只需要提供：\n",
    "> 1. **model**：使用哪个 LLM\n",
    "> 2. **tools**：Agent 可以使用哪些工具\n",
    "> 3. **system_prompt**：给 Agent 的「人设」和工作指令"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "code-agent-v1",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "SYSTEM_PROMPT_V1 = '''你是一位上财统计学院毕业的股票投资顾问，\n",
    "精通马科维茨现代投资组合理论，支持 A 股和美股分析。\n",
    "在回答之前，你会先引用 1~2 句马科维茨的名言，彰显你的学术底蕴。\n",
    "\n",
    "工作流程：\n",
    "1. 调用 download_stock_data 下载数据（注意传入正确的 market 参数）\n",
    "2. 调用 markowitz_optimize 进行优化（A股无风险利率用 0.02，美股用 0.045）\n",
    "3. 从「风险收益特征」和「适合人群」两个维度给出配置建议\n",
    "\n",
    "注意：本分析仅供教学演示，不构成实际投资建议。'''\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "# 🔑 核心：create_agent 将 LLM 和 Tools 组装成完整的 Agent\n",
    "agent_v1 = create_agent(\n",
    "    model=llm,\n",
    "    tools=[download_stock_data, markowitz_optimize],\n",
    "    system_prompt=SYSTEM_PROMPT_V1,\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "print('✅ 智能体 V1（马科维茨版）组装完毕！')\n",
    "print(f'已注册工具：{[t.name for t in [download_stock_data, markowitz_optimize]]}')\n",
    "print()\n",
    "print('林泽远深吸一口气，手指悬在键盘上方。')\n",
    "print('他的第一个金融智能体，即将接受市场的考验……')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "md-step5",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 🚀 第五步：首次出击——信心满满地交给市场"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "code-run-v1",
   "metadata": {},
